gobblin.source.extractor.filebased

Interface TimestampAwareFileBasedHelper

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable, FileBasedHelper, SizeAwareFileBasedHelper
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AvroFsHelper, HadoopFsHelper, SftpFsHelper

    public interface TimestampAwareFileBasedHelper
extends SizeAwareFileBasedHelper
    A File helper that extends SizeAwareFileBasedHelper and has functionality to get file modified time. This interface exists for backward compatibility of SizeAwareFileBasedHelper.
